<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Froth1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Froth,</orth> subst. spume, foam: <bibl n="shak. wt 3.3.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 3, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.433" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 433</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 5.1.220" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 220</bibl>. Metaphorically, == any thing vain and empty: <cit><quote>a dream, a breath, a f. of fleeting joy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 212" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 212</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>f. and scum, thou liest,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.167" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 167</bibl></cit>.
